0. for new morphology, put them into the subfolder with name 'neurons_<suffix>'
1. select the morphology (check/revise changemorph.sh script)
2. revise the morphology (if needed)
3. create symbolic link 'neuron.swc' to that morphology
4. gen spines  (created inside that morphology folder)
5. copy the spines folder to the main folder
6. move the neurons.txt file (inside spines folder) to the main folder
7. configure the GSL (stimulus, I/O, params)
8. run the simulation 
